>
>How much fluid do I put in the reduction boxes?

VW spec is 0.25 L, or 0.53 US pints, for each box.  They also say
that if you are doing the transmission and the reduction boxes at
the same time, to fill up the boxes first and then the transmission.

>Is there a fill mark?

Not that I know of.  I just did this on my '64 and I didn't see one.

Matt Roberds


